description: Syd Blakovich the Hungarian Nightmare is getting geared up for the Ultimate Surrender Summer Vengeance Tournament that starts in 2 weeks. Unfortunately for Amber Rayne she is the practice target. However this practice target did not give in, did not quit. The nightmare had her in many brutal submission holds and the Rogue never once gave in. You have to give props to the Rogue for sheer determination and grit, not to mention the brutal ASS fucking she had to endure from the Nightmare.
title: The Nightmare (7-2) Ranked 3th
